<pre>

To set up the yum repository for RHEL/CentOS, 
create the file named /etc/yum.repos.d/nginx.repo with the following contents:

[nginx]
name=nginx repo
baseurl=http://nginx.org/packages/OS/OSRELEASE/$basearch/
gpgcheck=0
enabled=1


Replace â€œOSâ€ with â€œrhelâ€ or â€œcentosâ€, depending on the distribution used, 
and â€œOSRELEASEâ€ with â€œ6â€ or â€œ7â€, for 6.x or 7.x versions, respectively.

</pre>

